The '''Nyakuron Cultural Centre''' (or '''NCC''') ni ikigo cya leta gifite kandi kigenzurwa gishinzwe kubungabunga,  guteza imbere sinema n’umuco muri [[Sudani]] yepfo <ref>https://www.petitfute.co.uk/v57983-juba/c1173-visites-points-d-interet/c958-musee/439936-nyakuron-cultural-centre.html</ref><ref>https://jubainthemaking.com/nyakuron-cultural-centre/</ref>.  

== Amateka ==
Centre ya Nyakuron yubatswe nyuma y’amasezerano ya Addis Abeba yo mu 1972, arangiza intambara ya mbere ya Sudani<ref>https://www.musicinafrica.net/directory/nyakuron-cultural-centre</ref> . Iki kigo cyafunguwe ku mugaragaro mu 1976 kiyobowe na Abel Alier<ref>https://jubainthemaking.com/nyakuron-cultural-centre/</ref> .  

Uruganda runini rwarimo ubusitani bunini, ikibuga cyo hanze, inzu yimyidagaduro, club nijoro hamwe na kazino. Benshi mu minsi mikuru yumuco yaho ndetse n’amahanga ikorerwa muri santere, irimo; Iserukiramuco ryamahoro rya Hagana, Iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Juba, igitaramo cya Kilkilu Ana, amarushanwa mpuzamahanga ya bokisi ndetse n’imurikagurisha<ref>https://yellow.place/en/nyakuron-cultural-centre-juba-south-sudan</ref><ref>https://www.efe.com/efe/english/world/south-sudan-laughs-its-way-to-peace/50000262-4025694</ref>. Uretse ibyo, iranakodeshwa mubikorwa byihariye nk'ubukwe<ref>https://www.jubamonitor.com/arts-for-peace-building-forum-aborts-at-the-last-moment/</ref>. 

